data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! Current Mortgage is assumable at 3.25% for qualified Buyer. Practically new home located in quiet cul-de-sac of gated neighborhood. Tile floors throughout main living area & freshly cleaned carpets in bedrooms. Kitchen features Quartz countertops, SS appliances, large island, 42'' cabinets w/ crown uppers & opens to family room for an entertainer's dream. Split floorplan offering privacy for both the Owner & the kids. Owner's Suite features en-suite w/ Quartz counters, dual vanity sinks & walk-in shower. Owner has added beautiful plantation shutters, upgraded lighting fixtures & fenced back yard w/ vinyl fencing for privacy. Three additional bedrooms & large interior utility room just freshly painted. Amenities include fitness center, pool & playground
